      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "content": "Squirrel Nutkin lived happily with his mamma and three sisters in a big tree by the lake. They were all together under a bright blue sky.",
      "source_page_number": 1,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_001.jpg",
        "filename": "page_001.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_001.mp3",
        "filename": "page_001.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "content": "Next, Nutkin and his whole family sailed across the calm water in a little boat. They traveled on a journey to Owl Island.",
      "source_page_number": 2,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_002.jpg",
        "filename": "page_002.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_002.mp3",
        "filename": "page_002.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "content": "They gave Old Brown Owl three field mice as a gift for him. Then they asked if they could gather many nuts on his island.",
      "source_page_number": 3,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_003.jpg",
        "filename": "page_003.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_003.mp3",
        "filename": "page_003.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "content": "Old Brown Owl accepted their kind gift very happily. Because of the nice gift, he let them gather all the nuts they wanted.",
      "source_page_number": 4,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_004.jpg",
        "filename": "page_004.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_004.mp3",
        "filename": "page_004.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "Everyone worked hard gathering nuts at the forest. But Nutkin did not work because he had other important things to do!",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
        "filename": "page_005.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_005.mp3",
        "filename": "page_005.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 6,
      "content": "Nutkin began dancing and told Old Brown riddles for fun. He thought it was so funny when the owl looked puzzled.",
      "source_page_number": 6,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_006.jpg",
        "filename": "page_006.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_006.mp3",
        "filename": "page_006.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 7,
      "content": "But day after day they came back with another wonderful gift. Still, Nutkin teased Old Brown more and more every time.",
      "source_page_number": 7,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_007.jpg",
        "filename": "page_007.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_007.mp3",
        "filename": "page_007.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 8,
      "content": "At last, Old Brown Owl warned Nutkin strongly to stop teasing him. The owl said that if he kept it up, he would be sorry!",
      "source_page_number": 8,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_008.jpg",
        "filename": "page_008.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_008.mp3",
        "filename": "page_008.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 9,
      "content": "However, Nutkin refused to listen and teased the wise owl one more time. Suddenly whoosh Old Brown caught him in his strong claws!",
      "source_page_number": 9,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_009.jpg",
        "filename": "page_009.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_009.mp3",
        "filename": "page_009.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 10,
      "content": "Nutkin wriggled and kicked fast because he tried hard to escape. But poor Nutkin left most of his beautiful tail stuck in the owl's claws.",
      "source_page_number": 10,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_010.jpg",
        "filename": "page_010.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_010.mp3",
        "filename": "page_010.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 11,
      "content": "Finally, Nutkin went home very quietly that day. He learned that being kind and polite is always the very best way to be.",
      "source_page_number": 11,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_011.jpg",
        "filename": "page_011.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
